344
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:28,880
You won't miss it.

345
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,039
And this one.

346
00:20:31,039 --> 00:20:32,799
P-Pediatrics?

347
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,519
Excuse me.

348
00:20:37,856 --> 00:20:39,456
Where is
