00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:41,880
Next to the water closet.

351
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,519
Water closet?

352
00:20:43,519 --> 00:20:44,200
Keep going.

353
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,400
Excuse me.

